Joon-ha
come back alive!

1:43:03.570 --> 1:43:09.970
Joon-ah!
You have to come back alive!

1:43:10.580 --> 1:43:12.200
Joon-ha!

1:43:13.440 --> 1:43:17.210
Joon-ha
answer me!

1:43:17.450 --> 1:43:19.180
Joon-ha!

1:43:25.420 --> 1:43:30.660
Joon-ha...
come back alive!

