Joon-ha
come back alive!

1:44:50.710 --> 1:44:53.400
You have to come back alive!

1:44:55.310 --> 1:44:56.470
Got it?

1:46:52.300 --> 1:46:55.930
Medic! Medic!

1:46:57.570 --> 1:47:00.770
Hold on! Hold on!
Breathe! Breathe!

1:47:01.510 --> 1:47:02.870
Stop it!

1:47:02.940 --> 1:47:05.740
He's dead! Retreat!
Get moving, you bastard!

1:48:10.070 --> 1:48:11.470
Joon-ha, you bastard!

1:48:11.810 --> 1:48:14.780
Where are you going?

1:48:15.250 --> 1:48:18.240
Come back!
Corporal OH!

1:52:22.730 --> 1:52:28.430
You haven't changed at all

1:52:29.300 --> 1:52:31.890
Just like in the past

1:52:33.600 --> 1:52:35.160
you're still pretty

1:52:38.610 --> 1:52:42.810
I've aged a lot

1:52:53.590 --> 1:52:59.620
- You had it hard, huh?
- Not really

1:53:07.970 --> 1:53:10.960
How's Tae-soo doing?

1:53:14.380 --> 1:53:16.680
I guess he's doing alright

1:53:26.390 --> 1:53:31.120
Why didn't you get married?

1:53:36.270 --> 1:53:40.330
Well, I did

1:53:48.850 --> 1:53:52.010
I heard

1:53:57.550 --> 1:54:00.350
I had so much to tell you

1:54:00.520 --> 1:54:06.050
But now that we've met
I can't remember

1:54:21.010 --> 1:54:24.000
It's a piano doll

1:54:24.150 --> 1:54:26.810
We have one
at my home, too

1:54:28.920 --> 1:54:34.860
When I look at it
it reminds me of you playing the piano

1:54:42.130 --> 1:54:45.300
It looks so much like you back then

1:54:46.270 --> 1:54:48.430
Doesn't it?

1:54:59.720 --> 1:55:06.780
We were so innocent back then

1:55:06.860 --> 1:55:09.850
But the past has gone now

1:55:11.030 --> 1:55:16.430
I think our feelings
took the best of us

1:55:16.460 --> 1:55:21.830
We cried and laughed
at the smallest things

1:55:49.400 --> 1:55:54.800
How do I look right now?

1:55:57.310 --> 1:55:59.570
You look healthy

1:56:00.340 --> 1:56:07.980
But I'd like to see
you look happier

1:56:12.590 --> 1:56:19.500
I'm crying right now
Can't you see my tears?

1:56:27.600 --> 1:56:32.440
Why did you hide that
you couldn't see?

1:56:43.090 --> 1:56:44.950
It's late

1:56:45.120 --> 1:56:47.750
Sorry, I have an appointment

1:56:47.930 --> 1:56:50.020
I have to go

1:57:43.150 --> 1:57:44.840
I'm sorry

1:57:44.980 --> 1:57:50.110
It was almost perfect
I could've succeeded

1:57:50.320 --> 1:57:56.120
I even came here
last night to practice

1:57:58.360 --> 1:58:01.350
You almost fooled me

1:58:02.630 --> 1:58:09.000
You did a good job
I nearly believed you

1:58:10.010 --> 1:58:12.200
Also...

1:58:16.180 --> 1:58:22.240
I risked my life to return
this necklace to you

1:58:30.530 --> 1:58:32.590
Please don't

1:58:36.130 --> 1:58:38.730
This necklace is yours

1:59:38.800 --> 1:59:45.630
Afterwards, mom and dad got married
And I was born three years later

1:59:47.740 --> 1:59:51.300
Then a few years later...

2:00:28.980 --> 2:00:30.950
Mrs. Sung Joo-hee?

2:00:40.820 --> 2:00:42.720
Joon-ha's last wish

2:00:45.160 --> 2:00:52.260
was for you to spread
his dust in this river

2:00:56.640 --> 2:00:58.540
Actually

2:00:59.480 --> 2:01:01.440
Joon-ha

2:01:03.280 --> 2:01:08.150
got married right
after you did

2:01:11.960 --> 2:01:17.390
Poor guy had a son, too

2:01:40.680 --> 2:01:45.950
And Joon-ha

2:01:46.220 --> 2:01:49.820
wanted you to have this

2:02:49.550 --> 2:02:51.920
Mommy, it's a rainbow

2:03:01.500 --> 2:03:05.260
I still remember clearly
the rainbow I saw that day

2:03:05.340 --> 2:03:09.860
Until I finished telling this story

2:07:11.580 --> 2:07:13.050
Open your hands
